Class CoinSpotClientV2

A typed System.Net.Http.HttpClient that abstracts CoinSpot API v2 calls and handles request signing.

Constructor for use in non-ASP.NET and/or integration and unit testing scenarios where Dependency Injection is not available and this class must be manually constructed. Requires only a CoinSpotSettings object initialised with your API Credentials

CoinSpotClientV2(IOptionsMonitor<CoinSpotSettings>, ILogger<CoinSpotClientV2>, HttpClient)

Constructor. Requires a registered Microsoft.Extensions.Options.IOptions`1 where TOptions == CoinSpotSettings containing your CoinSpot API key and secret

If you use the Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyInjection.IServiceCollection extension AddCoinSpotV1(IServiceCollection, IConfiguration) or AddCoinSpotV2(IServiceCollection, IConfiguration) this constructor will automatically be selected by the System.IServiceProvider
